"5:119:17" : {s: 5, a: 119, w: 17, r: "رضو", t: "رَّضِىَ", l: "رَّضِىَ", lc: 38, tl: "raḍiya", lb: "সুন্তুষ্ট হওয়া",e: "is pleased", b: "সন্তুষ্ট", f: 3, rm: "he was pleased/content/satisfied with him; regarded him with good will or favour or liked or approved him, choose/prefer, consent to, agreeable/acceptable, loved it, liked it, inclined to it, had a desire for it. ridzwanun - grace, acceptance, favour, that which is pleasing."},
